text: Đặng Khánh Lâm (born 23 January 1984) is a Vietnamese footballer who plays as a Midfielder for V-League club Hải Phòng F.C. and the Vietnam national football team. == References == Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Vietnamese footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:V.League 1 players Category:Xuan Thanh Sai Gon F.C. players Category:Navibank Saigon F.C. players Category:Hai Phong F.C. players Category:People from Hải Dương Province Category:Vietnam international footballers
